node.title: Homicide investigation launched after man dies in Waikato Hospital
node.description: Police have launched a homicide investigation following the death of a 57-year-old man in Waikato Hospital yesterday.
node.content:
["Eastern Bay of Plenty Police have launched a homicide investigation following the death of a 57-year-old man in Waikato Hospital yesterday afternoon.", "", "
File image. Photo: 123RF
", "The man was admitted to hospital on Monday after being the victim of a serious assault in Tāneatua about 2pm.", "Police were at an address overnight in Cobham Street, Tāneatua, where a scene examination will continue today.", "Police want to hear from anyone who may have information."]
